						<div class="postbody">I remember playing around with that idea a while back, the trouble for me was that I didn't know how to tell which cycle the PPU is on.  There's the /ALE signal, but that doesn't come out to the cartridge.  I guess a delay thing could be done, based on the PPU /RD or /WR signal, but I'm not sure of the best way to get that, or is there another way you have in mind?</div>

